89
00:05:58,000 --> 00:06:00,000
Sê gund in.
 
They are three villages.

90
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:03,000
Û kesên din tevlî we bûne li vir?
 
And did any other people join you here?

91
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:06,000
Çima na, ba'dî şerê alemiyê yekem,
 
Why not, after the first world war,

92
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:09,000
