them too... came from the north and settled with us. Meaning
it's been eighty years, maybe more.

96
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:22,000
Hemî malbatek in?
 
Are they all one family?

97
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:28,000
Gund gişk malbatek e û tu ferqek nîn e mabêna me û wan û em
