99
00:06:31,000 --> 00:06:33,000
Yanî bûye mervantî zêdetir.
 
Meaning the kinship became stronger.

100
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:36,000
Lê pêşî navê wê... Alû bû we gotî.
 
But at first its name was... Alu, you said.

101
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:38,000
Pêşî ew navê wî ah.
 
At first that was its name, yes.

102
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:41,000
Pişt re we çima navê Xalta li gundê xwe kir?
 
Then why did you name your village Xalta?

103
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:49,000
Bapîrê me, wek ez çawa bêjim... Xalta êla me ye, dîroka me
