Xalta is a tribe in Kurdistan, they are in Serhed,
particularly in the Serhed region.

105
00:06:54,000 --> 00:06:56,000
Her wekî ku ez dizanim, herêma Mûşê...
 
As far as I know, the Mush region...

106
00:06:56,000 --> 00:06:58,000
Mêrdînê jî hene... Erziromê jî hene.
 
They are in Mardin too... They are in Erzurum too.

107
00:06:58,000 --> 00:07:08,000
