114
00:07:35,000 --> 00:07:36,000
Tamam e.
 
Exactly.

115
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:40,000
Naha berî ev gund e, dused û pêncî sal e çêbû ye,
 
Now, before this village was built two hundred and fifty
